titleInfo.title: (PS) Korte v. Midland Funding, LLC et al
titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER signed by Magistrate Judge John F. Moulds on 2/26/13 ORDERING that Plaintiff's Request to Proceed IFP 2 is GRANTED; The Clerk shall send Plaintiff 3 USM-285 forms, one summons, an instruction sheet and a copy of the complaint filed 1/8/13. Within thirty days from the date of this order, Plaintiff shall complete the attached Notice of Submission of Documents and submit the completed Notice to the United States Marshal. The Clerk is directed to serve a copy of this order on the USM. Failure to comply with this order may result in a recommendation that this action be dismissed. (Mena-Sanchez, L)
